column5: I would try to help you, but i dont even know how to help myself, I would have just said the basic things like "its going to get better". The most i could do is try to relate to you or tell you my story.
If someones behind me i think they'll injure me, Once at school A girl passed me and smiled and I got freaked out.
I will think I did alright in a conversation and think back to it later and realize how much I suck at conversating with people.
